Forty. Yeah.

00:06:20.001 --> 00:06:27.001
I wonder...

00:06:27.371 --> 00:06:32.812
Hmm.
Ah, so it changed since then.

00:06:32.852 --> 00:06:35.612
Yeah.
Makio...

00:06:35.632 --> 00:06:37.492
What do we want first?
A pickaxe.

00:06:37.592 --> 00:06:40.052
Tsuruhashi Hideki.
Man, I'm just thirsty.

00:06:40.272 --> 00:06:43.532
I'm thirsty.
Would cigarettes work? No, honestly...

00:06:43.612 --> 00:06:46.352
I want a smoke so bad.
Still dreaming of a pickaxe?

00:06:46.412 --> 00:06:47.852
Hahahaha.
Like that.

00:06:47.852 --> 00:06:48.592
Hydration.
Right, first of all...

00:06:48.592 --> 00:06:52.432
I really want a cigarette.
You're just trying to break stuff.

00:06:52.532 --> 00:06:55.293
Well, yeah.
The second it's 'cigarettes,'

00:06:55.973 --> 00:06:58.553
