Then...

00:08:15.735 --> 00:08:18.056
Hello?
Ah, Makio.

00:08:18.576 --> 00:08:20.916
It was totally wrong.
Off by 40.

00:08:22.076 --> 00:08:25.416
What? Makio, you're free right now, right?
You have time, right?

00:08:25.976 --> 00:08:28.516
I'm free.
Could you go to Ueno Zoo right now?

00:08:28.656 --> 00:08:31.356
Whoa.
What?

00:08:31.436 --> 00:08:35.376
Seriously... Which is easier for you, Ueno
Zoo or Tokyo Teleport?

00:08:36.716 --> 00:08:38.696
Ueno Zoo is probably easier.
Ah, I see.

00:08:39.596 --> 00:08:44.516
Then go to Ueno Zoo and count how many
flamingos there are, please.

00:08:44.516 --> 00:08:47.277
Uh... yeah. Okay. Got it, thanks.
Latest count.

00:08:47.277 --> 00:08:50.397
You're really going?
He's going.

00:08:50.397 --> 00:08:51.717
Where to?
Ueno Zoo.

00:08:51.737 --> 00:08:54.297
Yes!
No, seriously, that's the least he can do.

00:08:54.377 --> 00:08:57.217
He should be doing that much.
Your attitude is nuts.

00:08:57.277 --> 00:08:59.857
At this point it is.
No, he's just dragging us down.

00:09:00.137 --> 00:09:02.037
He's not dragging us down.
Makio...

00:09:02.417 --> 00:09:04.877
What do you mean, dragging us down?
OK Google.

00:09:05.157 --> 00:09:08.677
