Play something that pumps me up.

00:09:09.857 --> 00:09:15.258
Since this will be a streaming show,
free-use music has been prepared. Hahahaha.

00:09:15.458 --> 00:09:16.758
Huh? What? Did it say something?

00:09:21.186 --> 00:09:24.246
That fits way too well.
This whole situation.

00:09:24.466 --> 00:09:29.447
Hahahahaha.
Am I going to die?

00:09:32.327 --> 00:09:34.607
Ha...
I'm shivering.

00:09:34.667 --> 00:09:37.467
What is this?

00:09:38.207 --> 00:09:43.628
This is the worst situation possible.
What is this?

00:09:43.728 --> 00:09:47.608
Hahahahaha.
Huh? Is this becoming a stream?

00:09:48.148 --> 00:09:49.148
Free-use music?
What?

00:09:50.488 --> 00:09:52.849
Isn't this supposed to be Wednesday
Downtown? Ah, I see.

00:09:52.849 --> 00:09:54.929
I was doing this thinking it was
Wednesday. Of course you'd think that.

00:09:54.929 --> 00:09:59.209
OK Google.
How does it even know that?

00:10:00.269 --> 00:10:05.430
We've made a special registration just for
today's shoot. Amazing, right? Whoa.

00:10:05.910 --> 00:10:08.230
Don't brag about that.
Hello?

00:10:11.810 --> 00:10:14.710
Ah, hello?
So, do you have time right now?

00:10:15.951 --> 00:10:18.231
Time?
Time? Uh, yeah, why?

00:10:19.511 --> 00:10:21.831
Can you get to Shibuya?
Shibuya?

00:10:21.911 --> 00:10:26.911
Shibuya? Right now? Yeah. There's a
pachinko place in Dogenzaka called Rakuen.

00:10:27.391 --> 00:10:33.132
I need the machine installed at machine
777 there. Huh?

00:10:33.212 --> 00:10:38.952
What? Right now? Yeah. It can be however
many hours from now. Please.

00:10:39.032 --> 00:10:40.513
Okay, fine.
That's hardcore.

00:10:45.093 --> 00:10:48.173
Why do they always go,
'Uh...' like that?

00:10:50.073 --> 00:10:52.454
That kind of thing
gets in your head, doesn't it?

00:10:53.514 --> 00:10:55.214
Can't be helped.
What a waste of time.

00:10:55.654 --> 00:10:59.154
It can't be helped.
You're a genius at finding flaws.

00:10:59.154 --> 00:11:01.594
Who even wants that?
I didn't care at all.

00:11:02.514 --> 00:11:06.875
Yeah. If there were just enough space for
one head...

00:11:07.815 --> 00:11:12.855
Don't they say if your head fits, you can
get through anywhere? What kind of master thief says that?

00:11:12.855 --> 00:11:15.795
People say that, don't they?
By the way, can your face fit in here?

00:11:16.576 --> 00:11:21.396
Right here.
Yeah, maybe, maybe.

00:11:21.396 --> 00:11:22.496
Yeah, maybe.
No, no way.

00:11:22.496 --> 00:11:24.096
No way, no way.
Seriously.

00:11:24.216 --> 00:11:26.116
No way.
Try forcing it in a little harder.

00:11:26.116 --> 00:11:32.137
But don't stick your head in too much,
because we need to eat that part. No, no, no.

00:11:32.217 --> 00:11:33.997
No way.
Surprisingly...

00:11:34.197 --> 00:11:36.717
I don't want a bald head there.
No bald head.

00:11:37.817 --> 00:11:39.337
No skin either.
What a visual.

00:11:40.358 --> 00:11:43.898
It'll leave scalp oil all over the path.
That'd be disgusting.

00:11:43.938 --> 00:11:49.198
I don't know why, but...
I wonder if they're simulating something.

00:11:50.518 --> 00:11:55.239
I don't think the human brain
can handle this much sweetness.

00:11:55.319 --> 00:12:00.859
Hahahaha.
This room has the worst vibe.

00:12:00.859 --> 00:12:08.300
Hello? Ah, Aki, it's Shinichi. All right.

00:12:08.300 --> 00:12:15.020
You know those things on roads where water
drains? Yeah.

00:12:15.040 --> 00:12:19.281
The metal grate ones, like a mesh, so your
keys don't fall through. Yeah.

00:12:21.041 --> 00:12:26.161
What's that grate called exactly?
The grate?

00:12:26.261 --> 00:12:32.322
The grate? I don't know.
Just look it up online.

00:12:34.542 --> 00:12:35.542
The grate...
Yeah.

00:12:35.542 --> 00:12:40.983
What's that thing called?
Are you exhausted?

00:12:41.343 --> 00:12:45.683
And it said something like it was good
too. One more thing: Umemiya Tatsuo Tsukemono Honpo...

00:12:46.683 --> 00:12:53.384
the Tacchan Doll...
Umemiya Tatsuo pickles?

00:12:53.624 --> 00:12:55.124
Honpo?
Rice field?

00:12:55.204 --> 00:12:56.204
Tsukemono Honpo.
Honpo?

00:12:56.444 --> 00:13:00.204
There's this thing called the Tacchan
Doll. Yeah.

00:13:00.504 --> 00:13:03.404
Find out how tall the Tacchan Doll is, in
centimeters. Okay.

00:13:04.504 --> 00:13:09.085
Please, fast. Sorry. I'll call again in
10... no, 15 minutes. Using too much.

00:13:10.225 --> 00:13:12.225
That was already six points.
We used too much.

00:13:12.265 --> 00:13:14.665
You really had the nerve to complain about
someone else's wife. True.

00:13:14.925 --> 00:13:16.905
You really said that.
Sorry.

00:13:17.025 --> 00:13:19.206
Stuff like 'uh...'
That one really was bad.

00:13:19.206 --> 00:13:21.086
That was the worst look you've made all
day.

00:13:21.226 --> 00:13:27.386
What now? Uh... if your wife goes, Shibuya
will take a while. Miyazaki-san...

00:13:27.406 --> 00:13:32.347
Should we take a little break? You've been
taking a break this whole time.

00:13:33.247 --> 00:13:36.867
No, we can eat while we think.
My brain's not working.

00:13:36.867 --> 00:13:39.647
Cup ramen...
I want some.

00:13:39.767 --> 00:13:41.748
What the hell?
Chocolate?

00:13:42.628 --> 00:13:44.568
Let's split the chocolate.
For the brain...

00:13:46.048 --> 00:13:47.388
True.
Need to get some sugar in us.

00:13:48.588 --> 00:13:54.649
Let's split the chocolate. And can we get
toilet paper too? That's your thing.

00:13:54.649 --> 00:13:57.689
No, we both need it.
There it is.

00:13:58.429 --> 00:14:00.009
One point?
Oh, that's big. Big.

00:14:00.109 --> 00:14:01.109
Ah!
Yes!

00:14:01.349 --> 00:14:03.429
That's huge.
Huge.

00:14:04.769 --> 00:14:06.510
It's chocolate.
No, this is great.

00:14:07.570 --> 00:14:09.510
I'm so happy.
Honestly, at this point...

