Heave-ho!

00:42:06.168 --> 00:42:09.368
No wonder you're happy.
And, and, and, and, and...

00:42:10.068 --> 00:42:15.049
So if it says, 'Find the key hidden in the
Candy House and escape'... Whoa.

00:42:15.509 --> 00:42:17.769
then it has to be somewhere in the Candy
House. This.

00:42:19.569 --> 00:42:21.769
Seriously? Does that mean we have to eat
it to make it appear?

00:42:22.329 --> 00:42:24.329
Whoa.
Whoa.

00:42:24.809 --> 00:42:27.690
Whoa.
This might be even worse than before.

00:42:27.710 --> 00:42:29.970
How are we supposed to find it? Seriously.
Ahh.

00:42:34.070 --> 00:42:36.550
What is this, where?
Where is it, seriously?

00:42:37.451 --> 00:42:39.711
Somebody...
Just open it already.

00:42:39.711 --> 00:42:41.211
Me?
Huh, a new escape...

00:42:43.012 --> 00:42:44.752
Um...
Here.

00:42:46.212 --> 00:42:48.993
A mysterious...
kind of ending, huh.

00:42:49.413 --> 00:42:52.233
Oh.
Yeah, the Candy House really is brutal.

00:42:52.233 --> 00:42:53.534
That was rough.
That was rough.

00:42:54.334 --> 00:42:57.514
After all that...
right when you thought it was over...

00:42:57.834 --> 00:42:59.795
Yeah. Turns out there's another mountain
to climb.

00:42:59.875 --> 00:43:02.515
Yeah.
Man, that's rough.

00:43:02.515 --> 00:43:03.515
And on top of that...
Yeah.

00:43:03.616 --> 00:43:07.576
Up to now, at least you could see how much
you had to eat to get from here to there. Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah.

00:43:08.376 --> 00:43:09.897
But this time there isn't even a visible
goal. Right.

00:43:10.217 --> 00:43:12.297
You don't even know where it is.
Man, that's rough.

00:43:13.697 --> 00:43:19.519
If I, Shinichi Omokuri Geinin, had a
partner say that stuff to me, I'd probably swing.

00:43:20.759 --> 00:43:24.119
I don't think I could take it. TV or not,
I think I'd throw hands.

00:43:24.319 --> 00:43:29.060
I'd just think, 'They can cut it out
later,' and... I might actually hit him.

00:43:29.120 --> 00:43:30.381
Hit him with the receiver.
Yeah, I'd hit him.

00:43:30.381 --> 00:43:33.481
With the receiver.
I really might not be able to handle it.

00:43:33.821 --> 00:43:38.262
If someone said that kind of thing
about... your own family on the phone...

00:43:38.262 --> 00:43:39.982
Yeah.
While slurping ramen beside you.

00:43:40.042 --> 00:43:42.883
That too.
His little sister was funny, though.

00:43:42.883 --> 00:43:45.863
Even the little sister didn't understand
anything. Yeah.

00:43:45.903 --> 00:43:50.524
She was just a woman who burned through
their phone-card credits. Right.

00:43:53.125 --> 00:43:54.205
And then at the end again...
Yeah.

00:43:54.565 --> 00:43:55.985
Well, a new...
a new one, yeah.

00:43:56.425 --> 00:43:59.746
It looks like a whole new escape challenge
opened up. Who do you think it was?

00:43:59.886 --> 00:44:01.006
Did you recognize the voice?
No.

00:44:01.666 --> 00:44:06.207
I couldn't tell from that.
It sounded kind of familiar, though.

00:44:06.207 --> 00:44:07.207
Yeah, something like that.
Yeah.

00:44:08.148 --> 00:44:11.208
No, I don't know. If they're carrying him
somewhere from there, maybe, but...

00:44:11.588 --> 00:44:13.749
Yeah.
I wouldn't like that.

00:44:14.749 --> 00:44:16.189
Ahh.
I see.

00:44:16.689 --> 00:44:19.210
So he has to get out from there?
Out of that box?

00:44:19.750 --> 00:44:21.390
Whoa, that's rough.
No, that can't be it.

00:44:21.570 --> 00:44:23.030
No, I don't know. Hard to say.
